data.description: Prepare to be mesmerized by this exquisite 2351 sq. ft. dream home! This cozy abode offers four comfortable bedrooms, two immaculate bathrooms, a main-level master bedroom, and a private fenced yard, making it an ideal place to create unforgettable memories. Furthermore, the property boasts an in-ground pool to relish during hot summer days, and a sophisticated enclosed sunroom with electric blinds - perfect for relaxation. Conveniently located just off Hwy. 96, this home offers easy access to an array of shopping and dining options.
